Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.38,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}why we all had come into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:59.39,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,0)\blur5\fax-0.1}I didn't know how to face the one beside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:03.22,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}only I looked away and wandered where to love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:06.06,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,0)\blur5\fax-0.1}though it was always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:11.44,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}If I have a tough, iron armor protecting the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.86,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}I wonder if I can see you, and beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.53,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}I just want to be stronger than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:22.45,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,0)\blur5\fax-0.1}to hold you, all of, oh even the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:26.79,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}All the dreams end up as mere dreams, even if game's over
